        "title": "fix(context-engine): forward isHeartbeat to afterTurn",
        "body": "The ContextEngine.afterTurn() SDK type declares isHeartbeat?: boolean but the harness lifecycle helpers never pass it. Context-engine plugins that check isHeartbeat (e.g. to skip persistence for heartbeat runs) therefore cannot distinguish heartbeat turns from normal turns.\n\nForward isHeartbeat from the attempt runner's \bootstrapContextRunKind through \finalizeHarnessContextEngineTurn to the ^GfterTurn call.\n\n## Verification\n- Existing tests pass (context-engine-lifecycle: 9/9)\n- Lint clean\n\nCloses #89302",
